data.description: This beautifully updated 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home is not one to miss out on. Walk into engineered hardwood flooring, beautiful tiled shower, granite countertops, all upgraded stainless appliances, and more. 3 large bedrooms on the main level, with a bedroom and a den area downstairs. Large laundry room with storage. Utility garage with workshop, completely privacy fenced in yard with another storage building in the back. Newer roof, brand new granite counter tops, new paint and appliances, new HVAC, and new gutters and gutter guards and a new water heater. Conveniently located to interstate access, shopping, medical, and more. Maintenance free and a beauty, call for a showing today!
